Guy Henry (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guy_Henry_(actor) 0 Guy Henry (born 17 October 1960) is an English stage and screen actor, best known as Henrik Hanssen in Holby City, Pius Thicknesse in Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 1 and Part 2, Gaius Cassius Longinus in Rome and Grand Moff Tarkin in Rogue One.
